National Football League Commissioner
 Roger Goodell  upheld the penalties he imposed on players
Jonathan Vilma, Anthony Hargrove, Will Smith and Scott Fujita
for their participation in the New Orleans Saints’ bounty
program.  To contact the reporter on this story:
